OL,3,CPSNI takes action against 74 officers
OL,4,Cover accessing body-worn camera footage
OL,6,FPolice in Northern Ireland have taken
OL,7,Fmanagement action against 74 officers
OL,8,Fover accessing body-worn video footage.
OL,10,FIt comes after an investigation by the
OL,11,FPolice Ombudsman which found they had
OL,12,Faccessed the footage without a
OL,13,Flegitimate policing purpose for doing
OL,14,Fso.
