OL,3,CPSNI takes action against 74 officers
OL,4,Cover accessing body-worn camera footage
OL,6,FThe footage is described as featuring
OL,7,Fan arrest of a member of the public
OL,8,Ffor possession of illegal drugs,
OL,9,Fduring which the arresting officer
OL,10,Fmade an error while administering a
OL,11,Fcriminal caution, causing a colleague
OL,12,Fto laugh in the background.
OL,14,FPolice Ombudsman investigators found
OL,15,Fthat between December 2019 and
OL,16,FNovember 2022, footage of the incident
OL,17,Fhad been accessed 248 times by 82
OL,18,Fpolice officers and one civilian staff
OL,19,Fmember based at 20 police stations
OL,20,Facross Northern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
