CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F441A1730374453
OL,3,CPSNI takes action against 74 officers
OL,4,Cover accessing body-worn camera footage
OL,6,FMost had accessed it once or twice,
OL,7,Fbut many did so more often, including
OL,8,Fone officer who accessed it 21 times.
OL,10,FFurther inquiries established that
OL,11,Fonly five police officers and one
OL,12,Fcivilian staff member had a proper
OL,13,Freason for accessing the video.
OL,15,FThe Ombudsman investigation concluded
OL,16,Fthat 74 officers had no legitimate
OL,17,Freason for doing so and two officers
OL,18,Fhad since retired and could no longer
OL,19,Fbe held accountable for misconduct.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
