OL,6,FAnother officer remains the subject of
OL,7,Fa separate and ongoing Police
OL,8,FOmbudsman investigation examining
OL,9,Fpotential criminality in relation to
OL,10,Faccessing the footage.
OL,12,FThe issue was described as having come
OL,13,Fto light during a Police Ombudsman
OL,14,Finvestigation of a separate matter,
OL,15,Fduring which usage of the PSNI's body-
OL,16,Fworn video system was examined.
