OL,4,Cover accessing body-worn camera footage
OL,6,F"A number of officers indicated in
OL,7,Ftheir responses that as a result of
OL,8,Fthe investigation by the Police
OL,9,FOmbudsman's Office they had refreshed
OL,10,Ftheir knowledge of PSNI guidance
OL,11,Fregarding body-worn video, which I
OL,12,Fwelcome."
OL,14,FMr Hume described the PSNI's decision
OL,15,Fto take management action against the
OL,16,F74 officers who accessed the footage
OL,17,Fwithout proper reason as a "reasonable
OL,18,Fand proportionate outcome".
