OL,6,FHe also welcomed the PSNI's acceptance
OL,7,Fof three Police Ombudsman
OL,8,Frecommendations to prevent misuse of
OL,9,Fbody-worn video.
OL,11,FHowever, he expressed concern that the
OL,12,FPSNI did not accept a fourth
OL,13,Frecommendation for a dip sampling
OL,14,Fexercise "to evaluate the scale of
OL,15,Funauthorised access to the body-worn
OL,16,Fvideo system".
