OL,3,CPSNI takes action against 74 officers
OL,4,Cover accessing body-worn camera footage
OL,6,FHe added: "Given the weaknesses in the
OL,7,Fcontrol of access to body-worn video,
OL,8,Fit is therefore our view that there
OL,9,Fremains a significant residual risk
OL,10,Fthat private and personal data can be
OL,11,Faccessed without a legitimate policing
OL,12,Fpurpose.
OL,14,F"On this occasion the Police Ombudsman
OL,15,Fhas taken the exceptional decision to
OL,16,Fshare these findings with the
OL,17,FInformation Commissioner's Office in
OL,18,Forder that they can consider whether
OL,19,Four insights can inform their work."
