OL,6,FDeputy Chief Constable Chris Todd
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Police Service of Northern
OL,8,FIreland expects all employees to
OL,9,Fbehave professionally, ethically and
OL,10,Fwith the utmost integrity at all
OL,11,Ftimes, and where it is perceived that
OL,12,Fconduct falls short of these high
OL,13,Fstandards, it is right that officers
OL,14,Fshould face impartial investigation by
OL,15,Fthe Police Ombudsman's office.
