OL,3,CPSNI takes action against 74 officers
OL,4,Cover accessing body-worn camera footage
OL,6,F"The police service has in place a
OL,7,Frange of measures to ensure officers
OL,8,Fare aware of their responsibilities
OL,9,Fregarding the legislative requirements
OL,10,Frelating to acceptable use and data
OL,11,Fprotection implications of viewing
OL,12,Fbody-worn footage. Anyone requesting
OL,13,Faccess to body-worn footage must
OL,14,Fprovide a 'reason for access' which
OL,15,Foutlines the lawful rationale for
OL,16,Freviewing footage.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
