OL,4,Cover accessing body-worn camera footage
OL,6,F"We have also recently introduced
OL,7,Fadditional safeguards including
OL,8,Fregular but proportionate dip sampling
OL,9,Fby line managers as well as
OL,10,Findependent scrutiny via our newly-
OL,11,Festablished service accountability
OL,12,Fpanel. We are satisfied that these
OL,13,Fmeasures achieve the same end result
OL,14,Fas that sought by the Ombudsman's
OL,15,Ffourth recommendation.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
